org.hibernate.ogm.id.impl

Class OgmSequenceGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.id.impl.OgmGeneratorBase
      • org.hibernate.ogm.id.impl.OgmSequenceGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurable, IdentifierGenerator, PersistentNoSqlIdentifierGenerator

    public class OgmSequenceGenerator
extends OgmGeneratorBase
    A JPA sequence-based identifier generator (inspired by SequenceStyleGenerator.

    This identifier generator is also used for JPA auto identifier generation. OgmTableGenerator is used as fall-back, if the current datastore does not support sequences.

    Configuration parameters
    NAME DESCRIPTION
    SequenceStyleGenerator.SEQUENCE_PARAM The name of the sequence to use store/retrieve sequence values
    SequenceStyleGenerator.INITIAL_PARAM The initial value of the sequence
    SequenceStyleGenerator.INCREMENT_PARAM The increment of the sequence
    Author:
    Nabeel Ali Memon <nabeel@nabeelalimemon.com>, Steve Ebersole, Lukasz Antoniak (lukasz dot antoniak at gmail dot com), Gunnar Morling
